fields.value: PDOC group encourages public to utilize the platform to address different health issues with special reference to Online appointment of doctors of different specializations,registered with us.We are also trying to update health information to an extent for awareness. For the time being at this pandemic situation we facilitate Telemedicine service (Appointment/consultation through telephone/Video call) which may be chargeable.free as per the conditions/specification of the physicians. We will try to help and promote each of the subjects concerned with utmost care to enhance the existing healthcare facility. However, beyond appointment and consultation, PDOC has no role to carry forward and hence not held responsible for the health consequences during the treatment procedure. Further,  the group must suggest accessing the severity of medical problem from both the ends before fixing a protocol for the patient.
